Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣你才感覺你是獨一無二的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yeah, so you can feel unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不只因為友誼而交朋友呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why not just have friends because they're your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annie Annie 我知道你在這兒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Annie. Annie, I know you're here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你對的 我是對Kelly動了心\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, you were right. I had a crush on Kelly.
