Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有好看的鎖骨\N{\fs38}{\fs38}She had these well-defined collarbones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天能盛水\N{\fs38}{\fs38}that could hold water in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒意識到我還喜歡這款\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I didn't even know I was into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不應該\N{\fs38}{\fs38}But I never should have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔那個勺子\N{\fs38}{\fs38}licked the spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是那個時候陷進去了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I got caught up in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么聽起來這樣 我怎么了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Why do I sound like this? What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是機器人嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Am I a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好很多了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到哪兒了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 說完了 但愿 - 等等 Annie 對不起\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Finished, hopefully. - Oh, wait. Annie, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我一開始就停不下來了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look, I just got started, and I couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 我根本不在乎那些\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Mike, I don't even care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 迷戀鎖骨太詭異了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, the collarbone thing was weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你今晚著什么魔了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}but what got into you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 我\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因為我對Kelly動心這事兒\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I just... it wasn't even that I had a crush on Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是在意Kelly對我有意思\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It was that Kelly had a crush on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得了這個病后知道還有女人\N{\fs38}{\fs38}It's just nice to know after all that's happened
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 覺得我有魅力 感覺挺好的 - 那我呢\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- that women still find me attractive. - What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我覺得你很有魅力啊 - 哦 那不算\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- I think you're attractive. - Oh, well, that doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 你還能怎樣\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I mean, what are you gonna do,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開一個受人喜愛身患帕金森的主播嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}leave the beloved newsman with Parkinson's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 要是這是你擔心的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Okay, if that's what you're worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算等你容貌逝去再離開你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I will leave you the minute your looks go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 謝謝\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'd appreciate that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你一晚都穿著這個嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Look... hey, have you been wearing this all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來真美\N{\fs38}{\fs38}You look amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我一晚上都想吸引你注意\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Yes, I've been trying to get you to notice all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過 你越看越美嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}If I told you you were beautiful every time you looked beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都無暇看別的了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}I'd never have time for anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真好聽\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That would be fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候 生活里你會左顧右盼\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Sometimes in life, you get turned around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了你是誰\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and forget who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我誤以為你是女同\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Sorry I thought you were a lesbian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 我原來也以為你是\N{\fs38}{\fs38}That's okay. I thought you were too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好棒 你們會親親嗎\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Oh, boss! Are you guys gonna kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在你的家人會在你身邊提醒你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Luckily, your family is there to remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才是質疑你\N{\fs38}{\fs38}They're the ones who challenge you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持你的人\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and support you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什么 愛你如初\N{\fs38}{\fs38}and love you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 伙計們 - 啥事 寶貝\N{\fs38}{\fs38}- Hey guys, guys... - What, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不見了\N{\fs38}{\fs38}We lost Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓噓\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Mike Mike\N{\fs38}Mike, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么找到我的\N{\fs38}{\fs38}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也是用遙控小丑魚氣球\N{\fs38}{\fs38}They're also the ones who will drive you crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼瘋你的人\N{\fs38}{\fs38}with remote control fish balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ian 把這東西弄走\N{\fs38}{\fs38}Ian, get that thing out of here!
